# SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0
# Intentfile — North-star contract for Gossamer
# Author: Jonathan D.A. Jewell <j.d.a.jewell@open.ac.uk>
#
# Committed next-actions ([[intents]]) and horizon aspirations ([[wishes]]).
# Non-gating — this is a progress report, not a hard gate.
# Run with: contractile intend run

@abstract:
North-star progress tracker for Gossamer — a linearly-typed webview shell with
provable resource safety. Tracks committed next-actions (Android CI pipeline,
arXiv submission, IDApTIK migration) and horizon aspirations (WASM ABI, L4 dyadic
mode integration, PanLL panel hosting).
@end

## Intents — Committed Next-Actions

### arxiv-submission
- description: Submit gossamer-arxiv-paper.tex to arXiv cs.PL / cs.SE via OU .ac.uk email
- probe: test -f docs/whitepapers/gossamer-arxiv-paper.tex
- status: in_progress
- notes: "Zenodo draft 19535676 already published as preprint. Awaiting institutional endorsement path."
- target_date: "2026-Q3"

### android-ndk-ci
- description: NDK CI runner to build libgossamer.so per ABI (arm64-v8a, armeabi-v7a, x86_64) + emulator smoke test
- probe: "grep -q 'test-android' .github/workflows/ci.yml 2>/dev/null || false"
- status: declared
- notes: "Raised as issue after 2026-06-02 Android session. webview_android.zig + jni.zig landed; CI build not yet wired."
- target_date: "2026-Q3"

### android-apk-pipeline
- description: APK/AAB assembly + signing pipeline (aapt2/d8/r8/apksigner, gradle-free)
- probe: "test -f android/build.sh || test -f android/Justfile"
- status: declared
- notes: "Companion to NDK CI. Gradle-free constraint."
- target_date: "2026-Q3"

### ios-appstore-signing
- description: App Store packaging, code signing, and notarisation for iOS
- probe: "test -f packaging/ios/sign.sh || false"
- status: declared
- notes: "Required to publish to App Store. UIScreen.mainScreen.bounds fix already landed (2026-04-03)."
- target_date: "2026-Q4"

### idaptik-desktop-migration
- description: Replace Tauri with Gossamer for IDApTIK desktop builds
- probe: "false"
- status: declared
- notes: "Staging decision required. Gossamer is the designated Tauri replacement per reanchor 2026-06-03."

## Wishes — Horizon Aspirations

### ephapax-region-modelling
- description: Model long-lived Android Service handles in Ephapax region calculus (cross-region Service→Widget refs)
- horizon: near
- why: "Service handles outlive Activity bounds; region calculus must account for cross-lifecycle refs."
- status: declared

### wasm-abi-target
- description: Compile Gossamer ABI proofs against typed-wasm target (shared surface with AffineScript)
- horizon: mid
- why: "typed-wasm is the shared compile target; making ABI proofs target-agnostic opens Gossamer to WASM deployment."
- status: declared

### panll-panel-hosting
- description: PanLL panels running inside Gossamer webviews (full dogfooding of the panel/shell relationship)
- horizon: mid
- why: "ECOSYSTEM.a2ml lists PanLL as dependent; the integration is the primary value proposition."
- status: declared

### crg-b-grade
- description: Achieve CRG B (formal CI green on all toolchains, no failing gates)
- horizon: near
- why: "CRG C achieved 2026-04-25 (16 README.adoc files). B requires green CI + no outstanding governance flags."
- status: in_progress

### affinescript-frontend-binding
- description: AffineScript frontend (@gossamer/api) used in a real shipped app (not just bindings/)
- horizon: mid
- why: "bindings/affinescript/ landed 2026-06-02 (PR #73/#74); first real consumer would prove the API."
- status: declared
